column5: Well, with the recent labour concerns, the economy and all the other stuff going on in the world, we sometimes forget the things that really make humans special. This performance really hit the mark with me, so in an effort to perhaps help some of you have a slightly better day, I am posting this link here. I hope you feel the same way I do... I found it really helped me get over the frustrations of the day. Reafirmed my human spirit! Enjoy!  HH
I like the thunder/rain effect they did. Really extraordinary to watch.
